00:46:00,920 --> 00:46:02,519
Saya tak tuduh dia!

483
00:46:03,639 --> 00:46:06,360
Seorang pegawai polis berjanji
akan tolong dia!

484
00:46:06,440 --> 00:46:09,000
- Itu saja. Dia tipu.
- Siapa?

485
00:46:11,000 --> 00:46:12,239
Polis yang mana?

486
00:46:12,719 --> 00:46:16,519
- Itu dah lama dulu...
- Tak! Polis yang mana?

487
00:46:18,159 --> 00:46:19,000
Nama dia.

488
00:46:24,920 --> 00:46:27,239
- Nama dia Dumont.
- Pengawal.

489
00:46:27,320 --> 00:46:28,440
Inspektor Dumont.

490
00:46:32,199 --> 00:46:35,440
Dumont memerangkap ayah saya
kerana dia percayakan awak.

491
00:46:37,599 --> 00:46:39,840
- Kenapa dia buat macam itu?
- Entah.

492
00:46:40,559 --> 00:46:42,639
Sudah lama saya cari jawapan itu.

493
00:46:44,639 --> 00:46:45,480
Assane.

494
00:46:47,000 --> 00:46:47,960
Saya bersumpah.

495
00:47:06,519 --> 00:47:08,760
- Awak nak ke mana?
- Dia sesat.

496
00:47:08,840 --> 00:47:10,760
Cantik uniform awak.

497
00:47:10,840 --> 00:47:13,360
- Pusing.
- Dia ikut laluan yang salah.

498
00:47:13,440 --> 00:47:15,880
- Pintu keluar di sana!
- Jangan berkasar.

499
00:47:15,960 --> 00:47:18,559
Saya akan lapor pada pengetua
tentang kamu.

500
00:47:21,039 --> 00:47:24,119
Maafkan mereka.
Mereka anak orang kaya, tapi bodoh.

501
00:47:25,280 --> 00:47:26,199
Benjamin Ferel.

502
00:47:27,480 --> 00:47:29,559
- Assane Diop.
- Selamat berkenalan.

503
00:49:06,679 --> 00:49:08,280
Boleh saya minta sesuatu?

504
00:49:10,039 --> 00:49:11,719
Buat isteri saya tersenyum

505
00:49:12,719 --> 00:49:14,360
dengan apa-apa cara pun.

506
00:49:39,519 --> 00:49:43,119
INSPEKTOR GABRIEL DUMONT
POLIS WILAYAH PARIS